00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,480
like these small rings.

294
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,670
I've already decided.

295
00:08:29,670 --> 00:08:30,200
Okay.

296
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,320
