304
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:40,470
Sure.

305
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:41,350
Just give me a second.

306
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:41,710
Thanks.

307
00:08:41,910 --> 00:08:42,440
No worries.

308
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:44,320
Here's your receipt.

309
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,440
Thank you.

310
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,880
Okay.

311
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:49,590
Thank you.

312
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:50,110
Thanks.

313
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:51,710
Bye.

314
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,590
Let's go.

315
00:08:58,350 --> 00:08:59,440
Are you nervous?

316
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,030
Not at all.

317
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,910
