318
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,400
Calm.

319
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,550
I'm calm right now.

320
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,590
Not sure about later though.

321
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:09,000
I might get nervous then.

322
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,110
But I'm not nervous now.

323
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,880
I just think

324
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,440
