325
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,000
The outcome is already decided.

326
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:19,590
What will happen will happen.

327
00:09:19,590 --> 00:09:21,400
What won't happen won't.

328
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,840
It's all been arranged.

329
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:23,880
(Believes in destiny)

330
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,590
So I don't really feel

331
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,640
nervous.

332
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,350
Did you just buy her a gift, right?

333
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,550
