341
00:09:45,350 --> 00:09:45,910
Yes.

342
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:46,540
(No hesitation)

343
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:47,350
She will.

344
00:09:47,350 --> 00:09:48,000
Definitely.

345
00:09:49,710 --> 00:09:52,350
Are you looking for
something practical or...

346
00:09:52,350 --> 00:09:53,230
Practical.

347
00:09:53,230 --> 00:09:53,840
No.

348
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,470
Both practical and meaningful.

349
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:56,960
Since he's a Taurus,

350
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,200
