351
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:01,550
I think earphones are a great option.

352
00:10:01,550 --> 00:10:02,790
But I don't know if he has

353
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,960
a regular pair already.

354
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,470
He said today

355
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:07,760
