357
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:13,350
He prefers talking in person
or on the phone.

358
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:14,960
So I think earphones...

359
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:16,110
Take a look.

360
00:10:16,110 --> 00:10:17,520
We can check out earphones then.

361
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,590
Or a Polaroid.

362
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:21,550
(Earphones or Polaroid)
And a meaningful little charm.

363
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,590
(Small charm)

364
00:10:22,590 --> 00:10:23,350
And then...

365
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:25,880
Add a ticket.

366
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:27,910
Next time I go to Singapore,

367
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:30,280
