can you take me to Universal Studios?

368
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:31,400
Sure.

369
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:32,550
Pinky promise.

370
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:33,550
(Hands on the wheel, stay safe.)

371
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:34,110
Pinky promise.

372
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:35,400
(Love matters, but life matters more.)

373
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:35,880
Pinky promise,

374
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,520
a hundred years,

375
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:37,400
no take-backs.

376
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,590
I think that works.

377
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:43,230
Hello?

378
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:44,710
Excuse me, where are the earphones?

379
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:45,840
Earphones.

380
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,000
Earphones.

381
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:47,590
Right here.

382
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,910
Which one?

383
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:50,470
This one?

384
00:10:50,470 --> 00:10:51,440
Just this one, right?

385
00:10:54,030 --> 00:10:55,520
He probably has AirPods.

386
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:58,000
That headphone...

387
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,550
Or maybe a watch?

388
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,110
But he doesn't seem to wear watches.

389
00:11:02,110 --> 00:11:03,620
(Sudden change)

390
00:11:04,470 --> 00:11:05,670
Would he like a watch?

391
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:08,840
I'm so torn. It's driving me crazy.

392
00:11:12,470 --> 00:11:13,590
I wanted to buy earphones,

393
00:11:13,590 --> 00:11:15,470
