394
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:18,710
I'll get the earphones.

395
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:21,380
(Finally decides to buy the ear phones)

396
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,200
Take this one?

397
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:22,640
Yes.

398
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,440
Do you think he'll like it?

399
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:28,000
And he'll say
he just bought this exact one.

400
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:29,860
(Oh no)

401
00:11:30,710 --> 00:11:31,710
And I'll tell him, then you...

402
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:33,670
Then just wear four earphones.

403
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,200
Thanks.

404
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,080
Let's go draw it first

405
00:11:40,220 --> 00:11:43,220
(Drawing Universal Studios voucher)

406
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:45,000
Next one.

407
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:49,910
