439
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:27,840
Hi.

440
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,960
Which one is Kuromi?

441
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:31,470
This one.

442
00:13:32,130 --> 00:13:32,710
This one here.

443
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:34,280
But it only has one small compartment.

444
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,960
It's not two pieces joined together.

445
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,000
Two pieces joined together?

446
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,440
Right, it only has
one small compartment.

447
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:40,500
(Talking past each other)

448
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,670
Just this one.

449
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:42,960
Are there any other Kuromi?

450
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,440
We only have these two for Kuromi.

451
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,320
No others.

452
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:46,470
This one?

453
00:13:47,230 --> 00:13:48,550
For this one...

454
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:49,760
Do you want the one over here?

455
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,320
I want the one on the right.

456
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,320
This is the right one, right?

457
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,000
Yes, this one.

458
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,080
Okay, I'll take this.

459
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:59,580
(Hurrying back to the island)

460
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:30,700
(Arriving at the restaurant one by one)

461
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,230
Last meal on the island.

462
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:34,760
Does anyone have anything to say?

463
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,200
I'll go first.

464
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,710
I think Guanjie...

465
00:14:38,340 --> 00:14:39,110
(Listening intently)

466
00:14:39,110 --> 00:14:39,710
When I saw you,

467
00:14:39,710 --> 00:14:40,790
I felt a connection.

468
00:14:41,230 --> 00:14:41,440
Yeah.

469
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,320
And I saw you grow

470
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,710
because you were really shy

471
00:14:44,710 --> 00:14:45,840
on the first day.

472
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,590
My name is Wu Guanjie.

473
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:49,350
And you can call me

474
00:14:49,350 --> 00:14:49,670
Guanjie.

475
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,590
Wu or Guanjie.

476
00:14:50,590 --> 00:14:53,280
I'm a bit slow to warm up.

477
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:55,080
So it takes me time

478
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,350
to get along with everyone.

479
00:14:57,110 --> 00:14:57,320
Yeah.

480
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:59,080
Slowly you

481
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,030
opened up,

482
00:15:00,030 --> 00:15:01,840
chatted with us,

483
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:02,760
and played with everyone.

484
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:05,230
Plus, you play basketball really well.

485
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:15,200
Respect.

486
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:15,620
(Admiration)

487
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,400
Thanks.

488
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:17,760
And then...

489
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:19,150
Yan.

490
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:19,790
(Me?)

491
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:21,230
When I first met Yan,

492
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:22,470
I thought she was fake.

493
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:24,520
Alright.

494
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:26,000
Everyone has that impression of me.

495
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,350
Like, she always had to sit...

496
00:15:27,350 --> 00:15:28,150
Perfectly straight.

497
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:31,700
(Footage of Yan being "proper")

498
00:15:31,710 --> 00:15:32,030
Yeah.

499
00:15:32,030 --> 00:15:34,520
And I felt her gaze
was really aggressive.

500
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:35,320
Very sharp.

501
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,340
(Couldn't hold it in)

502
00:15:38,230 --> 00:15:38,880
That's hilarious.

503
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:40,790
I just felt like this girl

504
00:15:42,230 --> 00:15:44,440
(Bestie, you're complex)
is complex.

505
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,030
Today, after

506
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,080
getting to know her, I realized

507
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,790
she's actually a pretty simple girl.

508
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,080
Too simple.

509
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,200
(A gorgeous goofball)

510
00:15:50,230 --> 00:15:50,790
Yang.

511
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:53,840
Actually, Yang has always

512
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:55,520
given me the impression of being

513
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:58,440
a very complex girl.

514
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:00,910
("Complex" sisters)
Our dorm is pretty complex, right?

515
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:02,030
With you, being complex means

516
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:05,110
that you have huge energy

517
00:16:05,110 --> 00:16:06,710
in a small body.

518
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:08,470
(Small body, big energy)
This energy is an aura.

519
00:16:08,470 --> 00:16:09,960
Any girl standing in front of you

520
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:11,910
will be overwhelmed by your presence.

521
00:16:11,910 --> 00:16:12,880
I really mean it.

522
00:16:13,710 --> 00:16:16,710
My bro is lucky to have met you.

523
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:17,150
Really.

524
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:19,860
(Agrees)

525
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:21,200
To sum it up,

526
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:23,440
I'm the oldest one here.

527
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:25,670
And my biggest takeaway is

528
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:28,710
that being with all you

529
00:16:28,710 --> 00:16:29,470
younger guys

530
00:16:30,230 --> 00:16:31,550
gave me more motivation

531
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:33,200
for the future.

532
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,110
I also hope in the future,

533
00:16:35,110 --> 00:16:37,710
if I can help you with anything

534
00:16:37,710 --> 00:16:38,440
or...

535
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:38,790
Yeah.

536
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:39,960
Let's just keep in touch.

537
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,030
I'll definitely help out.

538
00:16:46,230 --> 00:16:47,230
I'll go then.

539
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:49,350
And I really want to thank

540
00:16:50,350 --> 00:16:51,110
a few people.

541
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:52,320
Han.

542
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,590
Han, honestly,

543
00:16:53,590 --> 00:16:56,400
I've been changing how I call you.

544
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:57,960
Han.

545
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,790
Bestie.

546
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,470
Thanks babe.

547
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:04,400
That's how I am with friends.

548
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,800
I might be super affectionate at first,

549
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:07,590
and then slowly...

550
00:17:07,590 --> 00:17:09,190
but that's actually how I show

551
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:10,520
(I know, I know)
that I really like you.

552
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:13,710
And as for the boys,

553
00:17:14,070 --> 00:17:16,710
I'll start with Yanting.

554
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:19,950
At first, I thought you were

555
00:17:19,950 --> 00:17:22,310
just a playboy.

556
00:17:22,420 --> 00:17:23,400
(Laughs)

557
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,190
But later I realized

558
00:17:24,190 --> 00:17:25,400
you're really responsible

559
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,000
and attentive.

560
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,950
The time I felt it the most

561
00:17:27,950 --> 00:17:30,350
was during our party on the sixth day.

562
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:31,590
You were just over there

563
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:33,590
cooking for us and everything.

564
00:17:33,590 --> 00:17:35,400
I remember telling Yang then

565
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,920
that you're Papa Lu.

566
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:38,830
A charismatic man.

567
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:39,470
(Lu Yanting preparing the shrimp paste)

568
00:17:39,470 --> 00:17:40,070
A charismatic man.

569
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,760
Just a very family-oriented guy.

570
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:42,590
Bonus points.

571
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:43,560
Like a Papa?

572
00:17:43,560 --> 00:17:43,830
A Papa.

573
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:44,620
(Personally verified)
Papa Lu.

574
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:47,710
And Charlie.

575
00:17:47,710 --> 00:17:49,070
Uncle Charlie.

576
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:50,710
Okay.

577
00:17:50,710 --> 00:17:52,680
Never thought Uncle Charlie

578
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:53,710
is the oldest among us.

579
00:17:53,710 --> 00:17:55,040
Because when I first met you,

580
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:56,190
to be honest,

581
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,110
I also thought you were a playboy.

582
00:17:58,820 --> 00:18:00,900
("Playboy" brothers)

583
00:18:00,950 --> 00:18:02,800
But later I realized you're a

584
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:04,160
guy with personality.

585
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:06,310
You never seem to feel down.

586
00:18:06,830 --> 00:18:08,710
You're always in high spirits.

587
00:18:08,710 --> 00:18:09,640
