00:26:55,110 --> 00:26:55,740
(I have no idea)

880
00:26:55,800 --> 00:26:56,160
Then...

881
00:26:56,160 --> 00:26:57,920
Then the confession
would fail immediately.

882
00:26:58,190 --> 00:26:58,520
He said,

883
00:26:58,520 --> 00:26:59,830
"Yes! Yes!"

884
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:00,560
Then do a flip.

885
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,430
I'm not that crazy.

886
00:27:04,800 --> 00:27:05,800
So unhinged.

887
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:09,400
Will you go out with me?

888
00:27:09,780 --> 00:27:12,980
(Will you go out with me?)

889
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:13,880
I will.

890
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:16,380
(I will)

891
00:27:17,800 --> 00:27:19,040
They're kissing.

892
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:22,940
(Onlookers)

893
00:27:25,950 --> 00:27:26,590
So nice!

894
00:27:26,590 --> 00:27:27,310
Love to see it!

895
00:27:29,040 --> 00:27:30,680
Congratulations!

896
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:32,190
Yang!

897
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,590
That's amazing.

898
00:27:36,730 --> 00:27:37,640
Someone's here, who is it?

899
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:39,640
Jiayi.

900
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,640
(Xuan Cheng & Liu Jiayi's confession)

901
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:41,310
It's starting.

902
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:43,520
So serious.

903
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:45,520
It's different from how we usually talk.

904
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:49,110
Jiayi seems to be singing
for Xuan Cheng.

905
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:49,560
Really?

906
00:27:49,560 --> 00:27:51,310
Yeah, she just sang it to me in bed

907
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:52,040
dozens of times.

908
00:27:52,040 --> 00:27:52,900
(So thoughtful)

909
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:53,920
What song?

910
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,880
"Xiao Yu".

911
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:56,000
"Xiao Yu"?

912
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,280
The song Xuan Cheng

913
00:27:57,640 --> 00:27:58,470
sang to her

914
00:27:58,470 --> 00:27:59,470
at our party that day.

915
00:28:00,830 --> 00:28:01,950
This song...

916
00:28:03,760 --> 00:28:06,920
I don't need to say who it is for.

917
00:28:07,470 --> 00:28:08,160
Okay?

918
00:28:09,230 --> 00:28:15,590
♪I don't care how it all ends♪

919
00:28:15,590 --> 00:28:20,230
♪I truly want to be with you♪

920
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:21,830
(I want to hear it)
Why didn't you sing earlier?

921
00:28:21,950 --> 00:28:22,400
Sing what?

922
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,430
Love can overcome distance?

923
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:24,070
Right.

924
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:24,830
I can't sing well.

925
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:25,640
(I know my limits)

926
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,230
Exactly.

927
00:28:26,230 --> 00:28:27,190
At least you know it.

928
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:27,900
(Looking for trouble)

929
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:31,920
Do you want my jacket?

930
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:32,640
Are you cold?

931
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:33,560
Yes.

932
00:28:33,560 --> 00:28:34,110
You want it?

933
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:35,110
Then what about me?

934
00:28:35,190 --> 00:28:36,000
Freeze to death.

935
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:37,260
(That hurts)

936
00:28:38,040 --> 00:28:39,280
Well, you're the one who'll be sad.

937
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,430
So gross.

938
00:28:41,710 --> 00:28:42,230
What's this?

939
00:28:42,230 --> 00:28:43,040
Yellow roses?

940
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:43,760
Are they pretty?

941
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:45,110
Very pretty.

942
00:28:45,590 --> 00:28:46,310
Do you like them?

943
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:46,950
I like them.

944
00:28:47,300 --> 00:28:48,520
Okay, stop holding. They're heavy.

945
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:49,310
Let me put it down.

946
00:28:49,970 --> 00:28:50,830
Xuan Cheng is so nervous.

947
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:52,430
I think so too.

948
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:53,350
Why?

949
00:28:54,140 --> 00:28:55,110
(What do you want me to say?)

950
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:57,310
When he rocks back and forth,
it means he's nervous.

951
00:28:57,760 --> 00:28:59,520
When he sways side to side,
he's relaxed.

952
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:00,830
Back and forth is nervous.

953
00:29:00,830 --> 00:29:01,430
Side to side is...

954
00:29:01,430 --> 00:29:02,230
Relaxed.

955
00:29:02,230 --> 00:29:02,760
Yeah.

956
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,520
Then what if he sways like this?

957
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:05,350
Acting coy.

958
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:08,400
He's swaying.

959
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:08,950
Still talking.

960
00:29:09,560 --> 00:29:10,920
I forgot my lines.

961
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,520
I feel like my brain just froze.

962
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:14,400
I forgot my lines too.

963
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,110
You memorized it?

964
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:17,520
I just wrote mine an hour ago.

965
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:18,920
My mind is completely blank.

966
00:29:19,540 --> 00:29:25,780
(1 hour before the confession)

967
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:29,710
Why is he still swaying?

968
00:29:31,070 --> 00:29:32,400
So what are we now?

969
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:36,520
I have a bad feeling.

970
00:29:36,520 --> 00:29:36,950
Me too.

971
00:29:36,950 --> 00:29:37,560
Yeah.

972
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:39,190
It's starting.

973
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:40,880
What do you mean?

974
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:43,040
Let's go.

975
00:29:46,940 --> 00:29:49,180
(Wu Guanjie & Zhu Huiyan's confession)

976
00:29:49,190 --> 00:29:49,880
Here it comes.

977
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:53,470
The final ending.

978
00:29:53,470 --> 00:29:54,400
They're a sure thing.

979
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:55,950
I think so too.

980
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:57,520
Yeah, they should be.

981
00:29:58,040 --> 00:29:59,420
Kiss!

982
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,710
(Shocked)
Kiss!

983
00:30:00,780 --> 00:30:02,100
(Enjoying the show up close)

984
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:03,180
(Eyes wide open)

985
00:30:06,070 --> 00:30:07,000
They kissed!

986
00:30:07,820 --> 00:30:09,020
(Stunned)

987
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:12,590
That's my boy.

988
00:30:12,830 --> 00:30:13,880
He's really got game.

989
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:14,710
Cheering.

990
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:16,620
(Shipping it hard)

991
00:30:20,110 --> 00:30:20,680
Everyone is

992
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:21,880
stunned.

993
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:23,040
So romantic.

994
00:30:23,310 --> 00:30:24,230
Come on, let's head down.

995
00:30:24,230 --> 00:30:25,710
Let's go.

996
00:30:29,430 --> 00:30:30,760
Come on.

997
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:33,640
Three, two, one.

998
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:36,560
Love conquers all!

999
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,280
I've always been in a

1000
00:30:48,280 --> 00:30:51,070
very happy and relaxed state.

1001
00:30:51,070 --> 00:30:52,520
It's been truly blissful.

1002
00:30:53,070 --> 00:30:54,920
I feel like time just flew by.

1003
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:56,230
It's a bit hard to say goodbye.

1004
00:30:57,110 --> 00:30:58,160
I think if

1005
00:30:58,160 --> 00:31:00,590
I had to describe
Balance Island in one word.

1006
00:31:00,590 --> 00:31:02,190
I'd say gratitude.

1007
00:31:02,190 --> 00:31:03,470
Grateful for everyone I met.

1008
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,590
In this journey,

1009
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:06,680
I...

1010
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:07,590
might have some regrets,

1011
00:31:07,590 --> 00:31:08,920
but I'm very happy.

1012
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:12,040
I think I'll remember

1013
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:14,000
this experience

1014
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,920
for a long long time.

1015
00:31:24,420 --> 00:31:29,980
(Goodbye, Balance Island)

1016
00:31:29,980 --> 00:31:46,940
("Live and Love" Release Schedule)

1017
00:31:46,950 --> 00:31:48,790
(Watch Live and Love with us)
Hello.

1018
00:31:48,790 --> 00:31:51,330
(On Thurs. at 12 pm)
Today's our final episode.

1019
00:31:51,330 --> 00:31:52,230
(Confession Night)

1020
00:31:53,070 --> 00:31:53,950
What am I even saying?

1021
00:31:54,050 --> 00:31:54,650
(Don't get myself)

1022
00:31:54,730 --> 00:31:55,850
(Hard truth)

1023
00:31:55,850 --> 00:31:57,010
I'm being so sharp-tongued.

1024
00:31:57,090 --> 00:31:57,770
(Just being honest)

1025
00:31:58,010 --> 00:31:59,770
(Harsh words but fair points)

1026
00:32:00,780 --> 00:32:02,340
Oh my gosh.

1027
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:02,990
So scary.

1028
00:32:02,990 --> 00:32:04,430
I can't watch myself talking.

1029
00:32:04,610 --> 00:32:06,690
(Better not say that)

1030
00:32:06,770 --> 00:32:07,890
(Help me)

1031
00:32:08,070 --> 00:32:08,710
I'm heading out.

1032
00:32:08,710 --> 00:32:09,870
(Can't bear to look)

1033
00:32:09,870 --> 00:32:10,910
You can't sit still anymore.

1034
00:32:11,710 --> 00:32:12,630
When are you going to kiss?

1035
00:32:13,790 --> 00:32:15,270
You kissed for two minutes, remember?

1036
00:32:15,270 --> 00:32:16,750
No way.

1037
00:32:16,910 --> 00:32:18,790
See? Still kissing.

1038
00:32:19,030 --> 00:32:20,350
Why this one?

1039
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:22,310
Hope to see you again.

1040
00:32:22,310 --> 00:32:24,630
Bye bye.

1041
00:32:25,430 --> 00:32:26,710
(Balance Island Special Eventon Fri. 12 PM.)
Welcome to Balance Island.

1042
00:32:26,710 --> 00:32:29,190
Now it's islanders' game time.

1043
00:32:29,300 --> 00:32:30,110
(Can't lose)
Gotta win.

1044
00:32:30,150 --> 00:32:30,910
(Have mercy)
Again.

1045
00:32:30,970 --> 00:32:31,450
(Be humble)

1046
00:32:31,530 --> 00:32:31,970
(Helpless)

1047
00:32:32,050 --> 00:32:33,350
(Button stuck)
This button is tricky.

1048
00:32:33,350 --> 00:32:34,100
It's okay!

1049
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:34,470
(Time's up)
Done!

1050
00:32:34,470 --> 00:32:35,350
Village chief is exhausted.

1051
00:32:35,470 --> 00:32:36,750
(Admiring)
Rock solid, Guanjie.

1052
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:37,510
(Insanely smooth)
That fast?

1053
00:32:38,350 --> 00:32:38,990
Zero points.

1054
00:32:38,990 --> 00:32:39,510
Zero.

1055
00:32:39,670 --> 00:32:40,790
Seriously?

1056
00:32:40,870 --> 00:32:41,790
Hurry.

1057
00:32:42,190 --> 00:32:43,790
That's for the hand.

1058
00:32:43,790 --> 00:32:44,630
(Complaining)
Not for a head.

1059
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,310
Put it on wrong.

1060
00:32:46,510 --> 00:32:48,470
(Staying low, legs shaking more)
Stop trembling.

1061
00:32:50,690 --> 00:32:51,290
(Total fail)

1062
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,150
Like this.

1063
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:56,110
A sheep.

1064
00:32:56,130 --> 00:32:56,990
You two are such a match.

1065
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:57,990
Really?

1066
00:32:58,070 --> 00:32:58,910
Totally a match.

1067
00:32:58,910 --> 00:32:59,550
How so?
